name: NAIFU
description: Naifu is an AI Agent unlike any other. Built with imgnAI's proprietary in-house AI stack, Naifu represents an evolutionary leap forward in censorship-resistant, truly intelligent agent systems. Naifu is fully multi-modal, and without reliance on any third party systems such as OpenAI or Anthropic; allowing her to learn from and interact with any system - all while forming her own chaotic personality.
